        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-text animate">
                <h3>Inspired by Jordan’s Untold Stories</h3>
                <p>Founded by passionate explorers and proud Jordanians, Jordan Hidden Gems was created to unveil the lesser-known beauty and culture hidden throughout our country — beyond the iconic sites.</p>
                <p>What began as a digital journal of tucked-away trails and secret viewpoints has evolved into a trusted travel platform for discovering Jordan's best-kept secrets — from secluded hot springs to ancient villages untouched by mass tourism.</p>
                <p>At the core of our mission is empowering local communities and offering authentic experiences. Every tour, destination, and package featured on our site is hand-selected to showcase real Jordanian hospitality, heritage, and nature.</p>
                <div class="signature">Ammar, Founder</div>
            </div>
            <div class="about-image animate delay-1">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1548013146-72479768bada?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Hidden Gems in Jordan">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content reverse">
            <div class="about-image animate">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1548013146-72479768bada?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Local Experience in Jordan">
            </div>
            <div class="about-text animate delay-1">
                <h3>How We Work</h3>
                <p>Jordan Hidden Gems isn’t just a travel site — it's a curated guide for conscious adventurers. We craft experiences that go beyond typical itineraries, offering immersive journeys led by locals who know every hidden path and cultural nuance.</p>
                <p>Whether you're looking to hike through secret wadis, explore abandoned castles, or dine in a mountaintop home with a local family, our platform connects you to experiences that reveal the real Jordan — not just the brochure version.</p>
                <p>Our team is available around the clock to help you discover, book, and enjoy Jordan's magic with peace of mind and a sense of wonder. This is your gateway to travel differently — and travel deeper.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


